### Credential Hunting Checklist:

âœ… Check user Desktop / Documents for:
   - pass.txt / creds.xlsx
   - Notes / screenshots / KeePass

âœ… Run `findstr` for keyword scans

âœ… Drop + run `LaZagne.exe` all -vv

âœ… Manually check:
   - SYSVOL
   - web.config files
   - ProgramData folders (like RDPman)
   - Startup scripts / batch files
   - KeePass DBs
   - Outlook / browser stored creds

